name: Int8Array.BYTES_PER_ELEMENT
description: Returns a number value of the element size. 1 in the case of Int8Array.

name: Int8Array.prototype.BYTES_PER_ELEMENT
description: Returns a number value of the element size. 1 in the case of a Int8Array.

name: Int8Array.prototype.constructor
description: The constructor function that created the instance object. For Int8Array instances, the initial value is the Int8Array constructor.
